## ğŸ“– Overview

As part of **xFusionCorp Industries** DevOps security hardening, the system administrators configured **password-less SSH authentication** from the `thor` user on the **Jump Host** to all application servers within the Stratos Datacenter.

This ensures that scheduled automation scripts can connect securely to the app servers without requiring manual password entry, improving both **efficiency** and **security**.

